    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just so quiet now. the silence is heavy. i look at my old office or my phone and it's like i'm looking at someone else's life. you say it's natural to feel this way, but it feels more than that. it feels like there's nothing left to even try for. why would i even attempt to rebuild something that was clearly just an illusion?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
